  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  breast cancer

          -  desire for additional therapy with mistletoe extracts

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  contraindication for a therapy with mistletoe extracts(allergy, tuberculosis,
             hyperthyreosis, acute infectious disease, intracranial pressure in case of tumors or
             metastasis)

          -  current medication with glucocorticoids or other immunosuppressive therapies

          -  other concomitant complementary therapies

          -  prior therapy with mistletoe extracts &gt; 2 years or during the last 6 months

          -  karnofsky-Index &lt;60
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
